'''Gizka poison''' were small, [[Poison/Legends|poison]] [[Pellet/Legends|pellets]] that were used for eliminating [[Gizka/Legends|gizka]]. These pellets were very toxic and could [[Death/Legends|kill]] a gizka in a matter of seconds. They would also drive the creatures insane, causing them to attack other gizka in the area, infecting them as well and ultimately killing all of them.

